'''Haak-gaa-saan-goh''' (客家山歌) heh ngit zung saan-goh, heh [[Haak-gaa wun-fa]] geh zing-sui zi ngit, zi-yew lyuw-sing yi [[Kóng-tûng|Gong-dung]], Fuk-gen, Gong-si, Theui-wan dang thi-khi. Gaai goh zi-yew khaau hau-theu tsong-zok, tseui-yi yi tsut, heh Haak-gaa yim-ngok geh thui-biu.

